comments: Green (PHI) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Young's (ATL) arm, which does not affect his SQBR during his drive.
Embiid (PHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Curry (PHI) stops his forward momentum and releases from the contact with Huerter (ATL) at the end of his drive.
Embiid (PHI) is running alongside Collins (ATL) and makes contact with his lower leg, which affects his SQBR.
Collins (ATL) does not establish position in the frontcourt and then return to the backcourt.
From all available angles, it appears Simmons (PHI) makes clean ball contact to dislodge it from Collins (ATL).

Bogdanovic (ATL) and Embiid (PHI) mutually engage and disengage off ball in the post and marginal contact occurs, which does not affect Embiid's ability to receive the pass. Bogdanovic's hand gets briefly caught in Embiid's jersey, but he does not grab or pull it away from his body.
Embiid (PHI) temporarily loses control of his dribble during his drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs as he comes together with Bogdanovic (ATL) during his play at the basket.
Huerter (ATL) does not release the throw-in within 5 seconds.
Bogdanovic (ATL) removes his hand from Embiid's (PHI) path and marginal contact occurs as he slides his hand away during the post shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) turns and swings the ball into Capela's (ATL) vertical arm as incidental contact occurs during his play at the basket.
Curry (PHI) reaches in as Huerter (ATL) picks up his dribble and marginal contact occurs that does not affect Huerter's ability to make his intended pass.
Simmons (PHI) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Huerter's (ATL) arm, which does not affect his ability to cleanly gather the ball.
Collins (ATL) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) extends an arm towards Young (ATL) and marginal contact occurs during the free throw.
Capela (ATL) grabs and holds Embiid's (PHI) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Green (PHI) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Young's (ATL) arm, which does not affect his SQBR.
Simmons (PHI) removes his arm from Young's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Young's midsection before his pass.
Harris (PHI) cleanly deflects Young's (ATL) pass away and is legally allowed to go into the backcourt to recover the loose ball.
Simmons (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Young's (ATL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Collins (ATL) turns his body and marginal contact occurs with Harris (PHI) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined that a clear path foul would be assessed on the take foul by Embiid (PHI) to Collins (ATL) during the fast break.
Thybulle (PHI) reaches for the ball and avoids any contact with Young's (ATL) arm on his steal attempt.
Embiid (PHI) jumps A to B back into and makes contact with Collins' (ATL) body, which affects his play at the basket.
Collins (ATL) commits a take foul on Simmons (PHI).
Capela (ATL) makes contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm, which affects his shot near the rim.
From all available angles, it appears Green (PHI) makes clean ball contact to dislodge it from Bogdanovic (ATL) on his steal attempt.
Green (PHI) makes clean hand on ball contact as he tries to steal the ball from Bogdanovic (ATL) in the backcourt.
Collins (ATL) legally contests Harris' (PHI) jump shot attempt.
